===Etymology===
Originally referred to a lazy person, from {{etyl|enm|en}} {{term|slugge|lang=enm}}, probably of Scandinavian/{{etyl|non|en}} origin; compare dialectal Norwegian {{term|sluggje||heavy, slow person|lang=no}}.

